Theme: Mythological Creatures – 🐲

Challenge: Something has awoken deep beneath the earth... creatures, of all types and sizes, have emerged from the world's underbelly and are descending on human society. Are they friend or foe? We should prepare...

Create a scene in Decentraland showing what these mythological creatures look like when they appear 👹

From the tiniest sprites to trolls as big as mountains we want to see your version of these creatures appearing in the metaverse!


Build constraints:
Submission must be deployable on a 2x2 parcel scene with the following constraints:


✅ Height limit: 46m
✅ File Size: 60mb
✅ Poly Count: 40000
